     "titleFull": "Complete [STYLE] outfit floating in its exact worn position",
     "desc": "Complete [STYLE] outfit floating in its exact worn position around  an invisible body with every piece suspended mid-breath, mid-billow.  LOOK (bottom to top): [FOOTWEAR] → [BOTTOMS] → [TOP] → [LAYER] →  [ACCESSORIES] → [JEWELLERY] → [HEADWEAR]  FABRIC PHYSICS: each material true to its weight, wool hangs,  silk drapes, denim holds its crease, leather keeps its shape.  Every edge lifting slightly as if caught in one silent gust.  LABELS: hairline leader to floating label box. \"[GARMENT]\" uppercase / \"[FABRIC]\" italic / \"[ONE DEFINING DETAIL]\"  LIGHTING: soft directional from upper left + warm fill from below  catching linings and sole edges + cool rim outlining the silhouette. BACKGROUND: [COLOR] seamless, fashion-forward. TITLE: \"[LOOK NAME]\" elegant serif type, top right. SUBTITLE: \"[MOOD / OCCASION]\" italic.  Mood: high-concept levitation editorial, the outfit exists,  the person is imagination. 4K, extraordinary fabric fidelity, tack sharp.",
