     "titleFull": "A person standing alone in an empty white void, but physical",
     "desc": "A person standing alone in an empty white void, but physically attached to them by thin threads of light are roughly 47,000 floating printed photographs — the entire contents of their phone's camera roll — most of them are screenshots of text messages, memes, receipts, photographs of parking spots, blurry nothing, duplicate duplicate duplicate, only a handful are actual meaningful moments (a dying grandmother smiling, a wedding kiss, a newborn) and these precious few are buried in the mass, the person is bent slightly under the weight, the image asks without asking: what are you actually documenting, hyperrealistic photography, studio lighting, conceptual art gravitas, Andreas Gursky scale.",
