     "titleFull": "A colossal, hyper-detailed white marble statue of an Angel w",
     "desc": "A colossal, hyper-detailed white marble statue of an Angel with massive wings dominates the background standing in the middle, seamlessly carved into a fractured, icy glacial crevasse within a monumental brutalist temple hall. In the foreground, a lone figure in a red hooded cloak walks away from the camera, leading the eye into a midground populated by scattered, patterned marble floor. The artistic medium is a cinematic 3D digital render with the crisp fidelity of an Octane Render, blending classical Greco-Roman sculpture with futuristic sci-fi architecture. Bright, ethereal white volumetric light streams down from an opening above, casting soft shadows and illuminating mist around the base of the statue, creating a high-contrast teal-and-white color palette with an awe-inspiring, sterile atmosphere. The composition is rendered with an ultra-wide anamorphic lens, captured in 8k resolution with flawless texture mapping on the stone and hyper-realistic fabric folds. Add a glowing neon red FPV drone route line starting at the bottom right behind the clocked man with a circular marker and the word START, then curving upward in a smooth flowing S shaped path around the Angel sculpture, with arrow indicators along the route, ending near the top left beside the statue with a circular marker and the word END ar 16:9",
