     "desc": "Unreal Engine rendering, no watermarks or text. Cinematic wide shot of a cavernous indoor hall in a floating palace, ceiling lost in shadow, giant red lacquered columns receding into misty perspective. Deep depth of field keeps a lone Hanfu clad figure deep blue and amber robes sharp in the midground beside an open lattice window overlooking a cloud sea; pillars and rafters blur into monumental scale. Soft diffused twilight filters through silk screens onto a low platform where nobles play weiqi, tea cups steaming. Hanging calligraphy scrolls sway in the breeze; incense smoke curls from a bronze tripod. Window frames distant floating islands with silver waterfalls and pine groves. Reflective floor mirrors golden light; carved beams depict dragons and phoenixes. Palette: warm gold, ink black, jade white, cinnabar no harsh highlights, shadows in soft gradients. Mood: contemplative and epic, blending daily life with godlike architecture. --ar 3:2 --sref 2121792200 --profile ieo5ezo --sw 100 --stylize 1000 --hd",
