     "titleFull": "Two elderly scholars in muted indigo and charcoal Hanfu sit",
     "desc": "Two elderly scholars in muted indigo and charcoal Hanfu sit cross legged on a vast circular stone platform in a half open celestial teahouse, its roof supported by twelve towering pillars each carved with a different zodiac animal. Three open sides reveal a colossal palace complex rising from clouds  countless tiered pavilions with vermilion and gold upturned eaves catching pale rose dawn light. A mirror lake on a cloud island floats between them and the palace, reflecting the sky city perfectly, ancient lotus pads and silver green weeping willows at its edge. Smaller satellite palaces drift in atmospheric haze. The scholars are minuscule against even one pillar, tea cups dewdrop sized. Soft morning light casts long shadows across polished stone, illuminating floating dust motes. Colors shift from cool dawn blues and lavenders above to warm terracotta and bronze below. Wisps of cloud obscure the scholars' faces. A massive ancient pine grows from a platform crack, casting intricate shadows. Cinematic wide shot, shallow to deep depth of field, Unreal Engine 5, no watermarks, no text. --chaos 40 --ar 16:9 --exp 100 --profile novas9i tgnnslq --hd",
